These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, baking, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, videographer, lawyer, bartender
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, rock, funk, folk
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, dog, turtle
1. the videographer is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the fan of funk is the architect##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the videographer##1
5. the lawyer is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1
7. the videographer is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | cooking  | gardening | baking |
| Job           | videographer | architect | bartender  | lawyer  |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | funk      | reggae | rock      |
| Pet           | mouse          | pony     | dog    | turtle     |

