.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, almond-milk, fanta
There 4 different types of food: pepper, eggplant, pumpkin, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, d&b, electronic, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, handball, sailing, rowing
1. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1
2. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of pop##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of electronic##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
9. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | coffee       | milk | fanta        |
| Food          | peas     | eggplant       | pumpkin   | pepper   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | d&b       | gospel     | pop    |
| Sport         | sailing | rowing | swimming | handball |

