.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, almond-milk, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, scientist, fisherman, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, western, sports, animation
4 different pets are kept: rat, frog, horse, guinea-pig
 1. the person drinking water is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching western movies is on the right of the scientist##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the freelancer##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | juice | soy-milk       | water        | almond-milk        |
| Job           | scientist   | fisherman | freelancer   | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | western    | animation | sports        |
| Pet           | horse         | rat  | guinea-pig       | frog         |

