4. the project-manager is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the writer##1
7. the project-manager is on the right of the journalist##1
8. the argentine is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the hamster is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | writer   | journalist  | project-manager | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | indie | salsa       | reggae       | house     |
| Nationality   | british       | polish    | indian     | argentine  |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | hamster | goat     | bird         |

