.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, nurse, police-officer, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, western, horror, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, malaysian, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, badminton, sailing
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the project-manager##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
4. the japanese is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is the malaysian##1
7. the chinese is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
8. the nurse is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
9. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | project-manager  | police-officer    | nurse | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | horror      | western    | musical         | martial-arts    |
| Nationality   | japanese   | chinese     | malaysian          | argentine      |
| Sport         | weightlifting | swimming | sailing      | badminton      |

