.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, zucchini, apricot, cauliflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, teacher, scientist, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, musical, superhero, family
4 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig, rat, goat
 1. the person eating apricot is the person watching western movies##1
 2. the person eating carrot is the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the security-guard is the person watching western movies##1
 4. the owner of the rat is the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is the social-worker##1
 6. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the scientist is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | cauliflower | apricot     | zucchini |
| Job           | scientist  | social-worker      | security-guard | teacher    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | superhero  | western    | family  |
| Pet           | rat   | goat       | turtle       | guinea-pig      |

