.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, hot-chocolate, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, singing, photography, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, chinchilla, fish
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, helicopter, boat
 1. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade | 7up     | hot-chocolate    | tea |
| Hobby       | writing | photography    | skydiving | singing |
| Pet         | cat   | chinchilla  | fish        | rabbit    |
| Transport   | boat   | roller | subway    | helicopter |

